Interface HasGeocoderResult

All Superinterfaces:
HasJso
All Known Implementing Classes:
GeocoderResult
public interface HasGeocoderResult
extends HasJso

A single geocoder result retrieved from the geocode server. Note that a geocode may return multiple result objects.
